{"tid":1935285,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《南早》確診者曾與無綫記者飲酒 無綫新聞部13員工到私院檢測","createTime":"2020-03-20T12:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T13:56:56.000Z","uid":227801,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9bcd6d9581803fb982c82e085011ab6650a6a4bc","tid":1935285,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T12:39:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200320/60738037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200320%2F60738037&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXKHX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=af0274ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200320%2F60738037&h=a6e07682\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200320/60738037</a><br />\n<br />\n《南華早報》轄下Young Post一名24歲自由身女記者，在前日（18日）確診武漢肺炎，無綫新聞部員工今日收到電郵，透露上述確診者上周五（13日）曾跟一位明珠台同事到蘭桂坊飲酒；據悉，該明珠台員工為一名男記者，周日（15日）至周二（17日）都有上班，今日入住檢疫中心。無綫新聞部已安排13位跟他有近距離接觸的同事，到私家醫院接受測試，費用由新聞部支付。<br />\n<br />\n根據無綫新聞部員工收到的電郵，衞生防護中心今日已指令該名明珠台男記者入住檢疫中心，又指新聞部知悉事件後，即時找人消毒清潔他曾工作的地方。新聞部總監黃淑明另外向員工發電郵，指由於疫情嚴峻，除了已化妝的主播之外，所有新聞部員工必須在辦公室內戴口罩，並不應一起聚餐。"},{"pid":"fd6473069d9b892a67d774a8631ff8271055a7ab","tid":1935285,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T12:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50cbe52f507f3b0b345fc40135f04c39ac1c5b81","tid":1935285,"uid":277659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T12:43:52.000Z","msg":"蘭桂坊個源頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64f630510e8a0fb643ff105bf37655f89884e4d","tid":1935285,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T12:43:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=